Class  Game</H2>
<PRE>
java.lang.Object
  |
  +--<B>net.percederberg.tetris.Game</B>
</PRE>
<HR>
<DL>
<DT>public class <B>Game</B><DT>extends java.lang.Object</DL>

<P>
The Tetris game. This class controls all events in the game and
 handles all the game logics. The game is started through user
 interaction with the graphical game component provided by this 
 class.
<P>
<DL>
<DT><B>Version: </B><DD>1.2</DD>
<DT><B>Author: </B><DD>Per Cederberg, per@percederberg.net</DD>
</DL>
